{"id":144451,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：叙利亚大学生示威要求政改/","date":"2011-04-13T20:30:16Z","modified":"2011-04-13T20:30:16Z","title":"简讯：叙利亚大学生示威要求政改","content":"<div>\n<p>叙利亚大学生据报在该国北部重要城市阿勒颇举行抗议示威，要求政治改革。</p>\n<p>这是叙利亚自一个月前爆发抗议浪潮以来首次在阿勒颇市发生抗议活动。</p>\n<p>此外，数百名妇女和儿童堵住了叙利亚海岸高速公路，抗议当局近日逮捕数十名要求民主改革的示威者。</p>\n<p>参加抗议的妇女手持白布和橄榄枝。她们大多数来自叙利亚沿海的村镇。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/e089PQZS2Mhy7emaKGL1uoJcEeU/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/e089PQZS2Mhy7emaKGL1uoJcEeU/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/e089PQZS2Mhy7emaKGL1uoJcEeU/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/e089PQZS2Mhy7emaKGL1uoJcEeU/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/4-gUKaWDZQY\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？请电邮订阅数字时代 <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe me!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}